<i>adjective</i>: 후련하다 [후련하다], 환하다 [환ː하다], 시원하다 [시원하다], 시원스럽다 [시원스럽따], 거뜬하다 [거뜬하다], 개운하다 [개운하다], 가뜬하다 [가뜬하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>후련하다 [후련하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. refreshed; relieved</dd><br>
<dd>거북하거나 좋지 않았던 속이 풀려서 시원하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling refreshed because an uncomfortable feeling or heaviness in the stomach has gone away.</dd><br>
<dd>2. relieved; refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 답답하게 맺혔던 것이 풀려 시원하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling light and relieved because one's anxiety has been resolved.</dd><br>
<dt>환하다 [환ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bright; light; radiant</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 비치어 맑고 밝다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being very clear and bright as light shines.</dd><br>
<dd>2. open; clear</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 넓고 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something imparting a feeling of not being confined, because it has an open view.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clear; obvious</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일이 되어 가는 사정이나 속내가 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The progress or intention of a certain event being clear.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fine-looking; attractive-looking</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이 깔끔하게 잘생겨 보기에 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a pleasing, neat, and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. bright; beaming; radiant</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 성격이 명랑하고 밝다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's face or personality being bright and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dd>6. bright; light</dd><br>
<dd>색이 밝고 맑다.</dd><br>
<dd>Color being bright and clear.</dd><br>
<dd>7. familiar; knowledgeable</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상에 대해 잘 알고 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having an accurate and deep knowledge about a certain task or object.</dd><br>
<dd>8. refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>맛이 얼얼한 듯하면서 개운하고 시원한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling tingly, clean, and refreshed in one's mouth</dd><br>
<dt>시원하다 [시원하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cool</dd><br>
<dd>덥지도 춥지도 않고 적당하게 서늘하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Moderately cool, neither hot nor cold.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cool; hot</dd><br>
<dd>음식이 먹기 좋을 정도로 차고 산뜻하거나, 속이 후련할 정도로 뜨겁다.</dd><br>
<dd>Food being cold and refreshing and thus it is good to eat, or being hot enough to make one feel refreshed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. open; clear</dd><br>
<dd>막힌 데가 없이 활짝 트여 마음이 답답하지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something not feeling confined because it has an open view without any obstructions.</dd><br>
<dd>4. speaking without reserve; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 막힘이 없고 활발하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's way of speaking or behaving being unhesitating and lively.</dd><br>
<dd>5. clear; neat</dd><br>
<dd>지저분하던 것이 깨끗하고 말끔하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that was dirty being clean and neat.</dd><br>
<dd>6. satisfactory</dd><br>
<dd>기대나 희망 등에 들어맞아 충분히 만족스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something being satisfactory because it meets one's expectations or hope.</dd><br>
<dd>7. relieved; refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>답답했던 마음이 풀려서 가뿐하고 후련하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling light and relieved because one's anxiety has been resolved.</dd><br>
<dd>8. refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>가렵거나 속이 더부룩하던 느낌이 사라져 기분이 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling good because an itch or heaviness on the stomach has gone away.</dd><br>
<dt>시원스럽다 [시원스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cool</dd><br>
<dd>덥지도 춥지도 않고 적당하게 서늘한 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling moderately cool, neither hot nor cold.</dd><br>
<dd>2. open; clear</dd><br>
<dd>막힌 데가 없이 활짝 트여 마음이 답답하지 않은 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something not feeling confined because it has an open view without any obstructions.</dd><br>
<dd>3. speaking without reserve; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 막힘이 없고 활발한 둣하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's way of speaking or behaving being unhesitating and lively.</dd><br>
<dd>4. clear; neat</dd><br>
<dd>지저분하던 것이 환하고 깨끗한 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that was dirty being clean and neat.</dd><br>
<dd>5. satisfactory</dd><br>
<dd>기대나 희망 등에 충분히 만족하는 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something being quite satisfactory because it meets one's expectations or hope.</dd><br>
<dd>6. relieved; refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>답답한 마음이 풀려 기분이 가벼운 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling light and relieved because one's anxiety has been resolved.</dd><br>
<dd>7. refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>가렵거나 속이 답답한 것이 말끔히 사라져 몸이 괜찮은 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling good because an itch or heaviness on the stomach has gone away.</dd><br>
<dt>거뜬하다 [거뜬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. light; easy; simple</dd><br>
<dd>다루기가 간편하고 손쉽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Simple and easy to handle.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheerful; refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 가볍고 상쾌하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's body or feeling being light and refreshed.</dd><br>
<dt>개운하다 [개운하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. refreshed; feeling well</dd><br>
<dd>기분이나 몸이 상쾌하고 가볍다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind or body feeling refreshed and light.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plain; simple; refreshing</dd><br>
<dd>음식의 맛이 느끼하지 않고 깔끔하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The taste of food feeling refreshing, not greasy.</dd><br>
<dt>가뜬하다 [가뜬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. light; easy-to-handle</dd><br>
<dd>다루기가 가볍고 간편하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Light and easy to lift or handle.</dd><br>
<dd>2. refreshed; light-hearted</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 가볍고 상쾌하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Body or mind being light and refreshed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>